7
00:00:40,837 --> 00:00:46,822
[SPEAKER_09]: 4000 Mississippi Parkway, case number 40 B dash 2022 dash 01.

8
00:00:49,993 --> 00:01:08,439
[SPEAKER_09]: This is the resumption of consideration of the petition of MVP Mystic LLC, an affiliate of Mill Creek Residential Trust LLC, for a comprehensive program pursuant to Massachusetts General Laws, Chapter 40B, for a multifamily, eight-story apartment development, consisting of two buildings located in approximately three acres of land, 4,000 Mystic Valley Parkway, property ID 7-02-10.

9
00:01:08,979 --> 00:01:18,262
[SPEAKER_09]: This proposal will be developed as an approximately 350-unit rental apartment building, containing a mix of studio, one and two, two and three bedroom apartments, with 25% of the total units being designated

10
