00:24:12,545 --> 00:24:16,867
[SPEAKER_11]: That building is currently under construction at 305 Winter Street in Waltham.

238
00:24:16,887 --> 00:24:26,549
[SPEAKER_11]: So it has been my experience as the building safety official to ask for this requirement be written into the order specifically

