00:24:27,289 --> 00:24:52,173
[SPEAKER_11]: for the purposes of fire safety during construction, which is the fight upon the jurisdiction as well as the building inspectors authority under not only chapter 33 of the State Building Code, but also NFPA 241, which is the safeguards during construction reference standard in the State Building Code, which again is enforceable by the building commissioner and the fire hall.

